2. The hayaa of women and the jealousy of men is absolutely an issue. Women absolutely will ignore health problems if it means they have to go see a male doctor. Preventative care is not daroora. Think about what we do in the US for those of us without health insurance. We would only go to the hospital unless absolutely necessary, and sometimes it is too late.
